<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 shí hòu jiǎn shǎo le, shí hòu bù duō le.
 zhè shì jiè de yàng zi jiāng yào guò qù le. yīn wèi zhǔ kuài huí lái le.
 zài bù yào wèi shì shàng de shì guà lǜ, yào tǎo shén xǐ yuè.
 yào xué huì xìn kào shén, jiāo tuō zhǔ. yīn qín fú shì zhǔ.</lyrics>
<title>shí hòu jiǎn shǎo le 迦南915</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
